		measure 'Bank Charges - Rep' = ```
				
				    SWITCH(
				    SELECTEDVALUE('Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency]),
				    "SCD Base",
				    CALCULATE(
				        SUM('Securities Transaction Costs GA Fact'[Transaction Cost Base]),
				        'Securities Transaction Costs GA Fact'[Cost_Name]="Bank Charges"
				    ),
				    CALCULATE(
				        SUMX (
				            'Securities Transaction Costs GA Fact',[Bank Charges - Local] * [Rep Rate]
				        ),
				        USERELATIONSHIP('Fx Rate DQ'[FX Join Key],'Securities Transaction Costs GA Fact'[FX Join Key])
				    )
				)
				```
